```

When this fix applied, the test code now outputs

```
[2015-03-04 11:10:44] test.DEBUG: Watch it {"a":10,"b":"[INF]","c":{"d":"[NaN]","e":null,"f":"[-INF]"}} []
```

Maybe still not perfect, but something like this would be nice to have. I spent quite some time debugging something involving INF, and I would have noticed the issue much quicker if I would've been able to see the logging context properly.

Thanks.
